{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://rclone.org/\">Rclone</a> est un outil de backups open-source disponible sur Linux, macOS et Windows.</p><h2>Installation</h2><p>Vous pouvez l&#x27;installer manuellement :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">wget https://downloads.rclone.org/rclone-current-linux-amd64.zip\nunzip rclone-current-linux-amd64.zip\nsudo mv rclone-*-linux-amd64/rclone /usr/local/bin\nsudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/rclone\n</code></pre></div><p>Ou via cette commande si vous êtes sur Arch Linux :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo pacman -S rclone\n</code></pre></div><h2>Configuration</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone config\n</code></pre></div><h2>Configurer un stockage chiffré</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone config # Choisir &quot;crypt&quot; (11) comme type de stockage\n</code></pre></div><h2>Voir la liste des remotes</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone listremotes\n</code></pre></div><h2>Voir la liste les dossiers/buckets</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone lsd &lt;remote&gt;:\n</code></pre></div><h2>Voir la liste des fichiers</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone ls &lt;remote&gt;:\n</code></pre></div><h2>Monter un répertoire</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone mount &lt;remote&gt;:/ &lt;folder&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Monter un répertoire en tâche de fond</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone mount --detach &lt;remote&gt;:/ &lt;folder&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Démonter un répertoire</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">fusermount -u &lt;path&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Pour monter un répertoire avec un meilleur accès en lecture</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone mount --vfs-cache-mode full &lt;remote&gt;:/ &lt;folder&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Copier des données d&#x27;un dossier à une source</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone copy --progress &lt;folder&gt; &lt;remote&gt;:/\n</code></pre></div><h2>Copier des données d&#x27;une source à une autre</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone copy --progress &lt;source&gt;:/ &lt;dest&gt;:/\n</code></pre></div><h2>Synchroniser deux sources avec les mêmes fichiers</h2><blockquote class=\"callout quote\">\n                    \n                        <div class=\"callout-title\">\n                            <div class=\"callout-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div>\n                            <div class=\"callout-title-inner\">https://rclone.org/commands/rclone_sync/</div>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"callout-content\">\n                        <p>Sync the source to the destination, changing the destination only.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </blockquote><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone sync --progress &lt;source&gt;:/ &lt;remote&gt;:/\n</code></pre></div><h2>Chiffrer la configuration rclone</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone config # Set configuration password\n</code></pre></div><h2>Vérifier la correspondance entre source et destination</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone check &lt;source&gt;:/ &lt;dest&gt;:/\nrclone check --size-only --one-way &lt;source&gt;:/ &lt;dest&gt;:/ # Check rapide\n</code></pre></div><h2>Récupérer un fichier anciennement versionné dans un bucket B2 chez backblaze</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone ls --b2-versions &lt;remote&gt;:\nrclone copy --progress --b2-versions &lt;remote&gt;:&lt;file&gt; .\n</code></pre></div><h2>Supprimer les anciennes versions d&#x27;un fichier versionné dans un bucket B2 chez backblaze</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone cleanup --b2-versions backblaze-crypt:/file.txt\n</code></pre></div><h2>Déplacer un dossier</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone move --progress --create-empty-src-dirs --delete-empty-src-dirs &lt;source&gt;:/path &lt;dest&gt;:/path\n</code></pre></div><h2>Autoriser d&#x27;autres applications à utiliser rclone</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone mount --allow-other &lt;remote&gt;:/ &lt;folder&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Tester la connexion d&#x27;un remote</h2><p>Exemple avec Mega.nz :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone -vv --dump-headers\nrclone -vv about --mega-debug --dump=bodies --retries=1 --low-level-retries=1 mega:/\n</code></pre></div><h2>Voir la taille d&#x27;un remote</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone size &lt;remote&gt;:/\n</code></pre></div><h2>Regarder un fichier video distant</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone cat &lt;remote&gt;:/&lt;bucket&gt;/&lt;file.mp4&gt; | mpv -\n</code></pre></div><h2>Voir les fonctionnalités supporté par un fournisseur</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rclone backend features &lt;provider&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Rclone.md","fileName":"Rclone","title":"Rclone","comments":true,"permalink":"rclone","datePublished":"2021-06-07T20:36","dateUpdated":"2021-06-07T20:36","publish":true,"rss":true,"note":"78"},"__N_SSG":true}